{"tid":729923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海航董事長墮崖亡","createTime":"2018-07-05T03:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T14:31:55.000Z","uid":58358,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4b0b58d1017fd5e0b6206129273919bffeecce5b","tid":729923,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:39:46.000Z","msg":"市傳資金鏈出現嚴重問題的海航集團，傳來驚人噩耗，集團聯合創辦人兼董事長王健，周二（3日）在法國公務考察時，不幸意外身亡，終年57歲；外媒報道，事發時王健為拍攝鄉村風景而爬上一座高牆，不慎失足跌落15米深山崖，送院搶救無效。據估計，海航目前債務約6000億元（人民幣．下同），外媒早前報道，官方同意協助海航集資止血，詎料此時王健卻客死異鄉，難免引起外界揣測。"},{"pid":"2c5659a122608dbe9aff12a0a170c017bc8eeb66","tid":729923,"uid":23734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:44:10.000Z","msg":"占中的蝴蝶效應"},{"pid":"5682ea47478ebcdb403df76d6a8e9b04c0ef363d","tid":729923,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事發時王健為拍攝鄉村風景而爬上一座高牆，不慎失足跌落15米深山崖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蝗蟲遊客天性黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf492d6c384aacf2f37c9dcc303c9eed0cdad21","tid":729923,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5682ea47478ebcdb403df76d6a8e9b04c0ef363d","tid":729923,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事發時王健為拍攝鄉村風景而爬上一座高牆，不慎失足跌落15米深山崖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蝗蟲遊客天性黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:40:29.000Z","msg":"你覺得係意外咩"},{"pid":"b55be96bc99bc5443c9d2397146a3d9ef892c9e5","tid":729923,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:41:38.000Z","msg":"一定係詐死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398f402e3971ab5a0019a9629a2715a139fa0c1f","tid":729923,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2